info: `-- hero` can be used as homepage banner on your fastn projects.

`hero` is a new conversation experience via using FTD lang. To use
`hero` on your fastn package, add below into lines FASTN.ftd file:

-- cb.code:
lang: ftd

\-- fastn.dependency: fifthtry.github.io/gangaimaging.com
\-- fastn.auto-import: fifthtry.github.io/gangaimaging.com/FASTN/ds as ds

-- site-doc.header: Invocation:

-- cb.code:
lang: ftd

\-- ds.hero:  Give your hearts the love it deserves
cta-text: Learn More
cta-link: about/
image: $assets.files.assets.back-img2.svg
bg-image: $assets.files.assets.bg.svg

