-- site-doc.header: Properties:

Below are details of all properties of this component.

-- site-doc.component-property: `title`
type: Caption (`required`)

This is a default property of the `hero` component. It’s used to add a
title to `hero` component.

-- site-doc.component-property: `cta-text`
type: String (`optional`)

This is a default property of the `hero` component. It’s used to add a
click to action button title.

-- site-doc.component-property: `cta-link`
type: String (`optional`)

This is a default property of the `hero` component. It’s used to add a
link to click to action button.

-- site-doc.component-property: `image`
type: ftd.image-src (`optional`)

This is a default property of the `hero` component. Using `image`
attribute image can be added.

-- site-doc.component-property: `bg-image`
type: ftd.background-image (`optional`)

This is a default property of the `hero` component. Using `bg-image`
attribute image can be added.

